{"tid":2062322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳茂波：香港打個乞痴都對美國有影響","createTime":"2020-06-13T05:09:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T06:52:15.000Z","uid":125168,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"2c53b895a4366a7dd14f7008d35f4fc6e8229f4e","tid":2062322,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T05:09:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oOqkVY6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoOqkVY6.jpg&h=f0494ca6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳茂波回應美國取消香港特殊地位，指香港「打個乞痴都對佢有影響」，認為美國假如對香港實施金融制裁，如不容許香港採用美元結算，不但會影響美資於香港的龐大利益，亦會動搖他人信心。<br />\n<br />\n相關報導：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/186040714921338/posts/1474341072757956/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F186040714921338%2Fposts%2F1474341072757956%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrqEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=8ac06deb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/186040714921338/posts/1474341072757956/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n#國際政治<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/weatherjj/26682\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fweatherjj%2F26682&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrqEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=ad058647\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/weatherjj/26682</a>"},{"pid":"5445f37a41d119e8a05fb6f326febea872070bd3","tid":2062322,"uid":125168,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T05:09:48.000Z","msg":"你夠膽打死我，你拳頭一定會痛"},{"pid":"51e22adb517b1d8a81b08f874a02384f0b4927d5","tid":2062322,"uid":2054,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T05:11:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/550045/org/060d1417f09e4ce7863ae22d5ca519c5.jpg/C844PwiSLhY9HO-aWoOV5flkWrBFrjkz8LLLMPCyyzA?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F550045%2Forg%2F060d1417f09e4ce7863ae22d5ca519c5.jpg%2FC844PwiSLhY9HO-aW